This skill allows the character to knock down or stun opponents by running or charging over them. This can be effective as an interruption tactic or to create chaos among enemy ranks.

A more powerful version of trampling, this skill enhances the character's ability to overpower and disrupt their opponents. It can cause multiple stuns and damage in a wider area and can be a decisive skill in the heat of battle.

The deadliest form of trampling, this skill applies brutal force and inflicts severe damage on opponents in its path. With a high chance of instant kill or critical damage, it is a fearsome skill to use when facing overwhelming odds or powerful enemies.
